  "detailed_description": "Bit Tower is a simple Tower Defense game where you defend your castle while trying to withstand increasingly larger waves. Hire adventurers, position them strategically, and fight against the waves of monsters.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594470/extras/7a49d23673301e984628616641f6324f.avif?t=1722984477\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play with 7 unlockable characters.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594470/extras/d89c6912b4bd77cfc0e5f129b4a8fad5.poster.avif?t=1722984477\" width=600 height=102 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594470/extras/d89c6912b4bd77cfc0e5f129b4a8fad5.webm?t=1722984477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594470/extras/d89c6912b4bd77cfc0e5f129b4a8fad5.mp4?t=1722984477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Battle against 4 species of monsters and their variants.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594470/extras/fa0fc10488c345532dcd48c0e275604f.poster.avif?t=1722984477\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594470/extras/fa0fc10488c345532dcd48c0e275604f.webm?t=1722984477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594470/extras/fa0fc10488c345532dcd48c0e275604f.mp4?t=1722984477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Support abilities.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594470/extras/e7d8c4a45892e3c853339d2e6c9f385a.poster.avif?t=1722984477\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594470/extras/e7d8c4a45892e3c853339d2e6c9f385a.webm?t=1722984477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594470/extras/e7d8c4a45892e3c853339d2e6c9f385a.mp4?t=1722984477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Unlock all Steam achievements.<br></li><li>Infinite waves, endure as long as you can.<br></li><li>Simple and fun game with 30 minutes guaranteed.</li></ul>",
